{"tid":802371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人生癌","createTime":"2018-09-01T12:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T13:32:26.000Z","uid":205672,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8892248217da17861c6b8be1cdd83891fc666b2","tid":802371,"uid":205672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"佢係我婆婆 一直都冇咩病痛<br />\n前幾日佢話個肝痛就去身體檢查<br />\n竟然有肝癌仲要係晚期<br />\n<br />\n佢今年先65歲佢老竇都健在<br />\n我以為佢可以睇住我長大佢仲話娶到老婆要俾佢睇下<br />\n我真係冇諗過呢種事會發生在我身上<br />\n<br />\n上網睇完肝癌末期條命應該得返一年<br />\n冇得醫介入治療最多可以有多三年命<br />\n上網睇左應該都冇咩方法可以醫到<br />\n如果可以我都想捐個肝都俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自細就係佢養我同佢感情仲好過老竇老母<br />\n但係而家竟然只剩下咁少時間<br />\n細個同佢講過嘅嘢佢一樣都未見到就要走<br />\n<br />\n一年前佢同阿爺返鄉下住<br />\n果次佢走我都喊到仆街<br />\n唯有同佢日日FaceTime<br />\n<br />\n但係今次係以後都冇得見<br />\n冇得再聽到佢叫我返屋企食飯<br />\n冇得再食佢煮嘅餸<br />\n<br />\n原來死亡離我哋咁近<br />\n一個好地地嘅人咁就會死<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得長我喺度講聲對唔住希望見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc036cc7523771303a5da185775818e2d0b3369","tid":802371,"uid":200258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534b79ca911c4611854770e5c8fdda598b345e9f","tid":802371,"uid":168331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:29:14.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0f50887135dfb56d2e2de4528a6459f4abacf7","tid":802371,"uid":205742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"多啲陪屋企人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  阿爸肺can未期一食緊標粑"},{"pid":"df54229700bf52502ac09864fa5d07597a3576dc","tid":802371,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"末期定三期"},{"pid":"7d4858da85668486e3c27f9684c229d9148db74c","tid":802371,"uid":205672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df54229700bf52502ac09864fa5d07597a3576dc","tid":802371,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"末期定三期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"晚期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f856808ee6c0c7b996413fcc74b2f6378e06ec1e","tid":802371,"uid":205672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b0f50887135dfb56d2e2de4528a6459f4abacf7","tid":802371,"uid":205742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"多啲陪屋企人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  阿爸肺can未期一食緊標粑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:13:52.000Z","msg":"巴打都要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699f5e3aef6213c936e5725f590ad6649f67dd87","tid":802371,"uid":188543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}